Clean GEE Output Data

Reviewing GEE Output Data

Now we will navigate to the data exported by our GEE Script. We now have 31 Landsat 8 SR Images. Although we can be very sure that these images are of high quality, it is always useful to review these images manually.

if (!require("raster")) install.packages("raster")

## Loading required package: sp
library("raster")
